divs: sighting detailsi am looking for some answers or information regarding pictures i've taken of the sun, and what appears to be black objects that stay near the sun. i've taken several different pictures over the last week, between 4\15 to present, at different times and different locations. the objects number from one to over twenty in the various pictures, and i don't know if this is a flaw in my phone's camera, or if i'm actually seeing objects near the sun. i'd like someone to look at the pictures i've taken and please give me some feedback. we have been seeing unidentified things in the sky very regularly and i'm curious. thanks!
Summary: Objects appearing in front of the Sun
